<translation id="8274659559228306809">{COUNT,plural, =0{A new update for AIWize is available and will be applied as soon as you relaunch.}=1{A new update for AIWize is available and will be applied as soon as you relaunch. Your Private window won't reopen.}other{A new update for AIWize is available and will be applied as soon as you relaunch. Your # Private windows won't reopen.}}</translation>
