<translation id="2176087127109773485">You can manage your signed-in AIWize sync chains. Your AIWize sync chains are used for AIWize browser, Play Store, Gmail and more. If you want to add an account for someone else, like a family member, add a new profile to your <ph name="DEVICE_TYPE"/> instead. <ph name="LINK_BEGIN"/>Learn more<ph name="LINK_END"/></translation>
<translation id="79269250264141507">When you type in the address bar or search box, AIWize sends what you type to your default search engine to get better suggestions. This is off in Private.</translation>
<translation id="3739288578188828252">When you type in the address bar or search box, AIWize sends what you type to Google Drive to get item suggestions. This is off in Private.</translation>
<translation id="2589970573128789862">AIWize Private</translation>
<translation id="5994282802285556682">When browsing in Private mode, AIWize will warn you before loading a site using an insecure connection</translation>
